snippet.title: Let's Play: Mini Car Racing - Part 2 - League B
snippet.description:
Part 2 of my Let's Play of Mini Car Racing Version 1.0; a racing game released in the early 2000s for Windows 95/98.

Played with Wine 1.7.16.
Game-play captured with SimpleScreenRecorder 0.2.0.
Sound recording and editing in Audacity 2.0.4.
Video editing in Kdenlive Version 0.9.6.
All running on Fedora 20 (Heisenbug) 64-bit (Linux Kernel Version: 3.14.2-200.fc20.x86_64).
